.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n捐返入你老母個閪度啦傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思話自己係肥v年代既人，智商仲低過08小隊打後果班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760fd065a457b6b997e66a39dbcda1c177a1736f","tid":207833,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"宜家啲廢青，一把斧頭都打唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你哋口中嘅廢老想當拎住支木杖不之殺咗幾多蘿蔔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申廢青，未睇內文"},{"pid":"d7eec2b54985df8aebcac6bd3f52812921612c26","tid":207833,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"俾人打劫緊係俾曬啲錢個賊啦，加埋先俾人粒走8千，咁大間公司驚閪咩，跟本唔當個8千係咩，況愈又有買保險，最緊要係員工條命仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申前7仔員工"},{"pid":"873241e2cd43789ad2f3def260f835dea3e1e175","tid":207833,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司被人打劫要個職員賠返<br />\n係咪做奴隸做上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正一奴隸獸，明明自己係廢青一名但又覺得自己係老闆，天下間竟然有此on9人。"},{"pid":"a0b64bc8a779907763e4db702011f3aadb56d1e8","tid":207833,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19994794&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily